attributes.title: EARLY SEQUEL PREP - Breath of the Wild PART 1
attributes.description: Breath of the Wild is getting a sequel so we are going to play through the original to celebrate such glorious news!

attributes.title: THE DOOM MOVIE SEQUEL - Doom PART 1
attributes.description: Blaine has been dealing with a lot of stress and pressure so we decided to play a calming game to bring balance and tranquility to his life. Doom is that game.

attributes.title: NINJA TURTLES 3: LOST IN SEKIRO - Sekiro PART 1
attributes.description: We did not ask Cole to come play Sekiro with Blaine & Jon just because he has played through it before and would be able to get past parts that those two are too bad to beat. We also asked him because he's our friend.

attributes.title: HOW TO NAME A HORSE - Breath of the Wild PART 2
attributes.description: Game objectives: finish the spirit temples, get the glider, go find Zelda. Mariel objectives: get a horse.

attributes.title: TEACHING ALIENS HOW TO COOK - Cooking Simulator
attributes.description: Jon has been abducted by two aliens who are forcing him to teach them the ways of humans so that they may understand our ways right before destroying the entire human race. Today's lesson: baked trout.

attributes.title: WE LOST THICCUMS - Breath of the Wild PART 3
attributes.description: At one point we had a horse. But then the horse kept moving like it was drunk. So we lost the horse. Now we don't have a horse. Sorry.

attributes.title: DO THEY SWEAR IN SMASH BROS? - Smash Bros. Ultimate PART 1
attributes.description: The Derp Crew joins the Rooster Teeth crew for some wholesome smashing.

attributes.title: THE DADS OF WAR ARE HERE - God of War PART 1
attributes.description: Who better to play through Dad of War than two cool dads who totally play the cool video games and know what is hip and cool?

attributes.title: TOO NINTENDUDES TOO FURIOUS - Mario Kart 8 PART 1
attributes.description: The Nintendudes take a stab at Mario Kart 8. It goes about as good as you'd expect.

attributes.title: BLAINE HATES MARIO KART - Mario Kart 8 PART 2
attributes.description: Blaine is very good at Mario Kart. But Mario Kart makes Blaine anxious. So Blaine hates Mario Kart. And we all hate Blaine hating Mario Kart.

attributes.title: THE GREAT BATHROOM SCARE - Layers of Fear PART 1
attributes.description: Barbara and Mariel co-op play Layers of Fear while Jon manages to scare them on accident outside of the game.

attributes.title: IT WAS THE FINAL SCARE - Layers of Fear PART 2
attributes.description: You would think that if two people were controlling a single player game they would get through it twice as fast. You would be wrong. You would be very, very wrong.

attributes.title: STAH WAHS! - Star Wars Battlefront PART 1
attributes.description: Time to win the Star Wars! And who better to win it for the empire than one beefed up Stormtrooper, Blaine, and his droid friend, Chris.

attributes.title: HAPPY BIRTHDAY JAR JAR - Star Wars Battlefront PART 2
attributes.description: It is Phantom Menace's birthday, thus it is Jar Jar Bink's birthday, thus today is a cursed day.

attributes.title: GIT GUD OR GIT PUNISHED - Star Wars Battlefront PART 3
attributes.description: It turns out Chris isn't so good at playing video games. We are going to attempt using immersive therapy to fix that. We are not confident it is going to work.

attributes.title: THE END OF STAR WARS - Star Wars Battlefront 2 PART 4
attributes.description: The time has come for the Empire to claim it's final victory in Star Wars Battlefront 2 and it turns out, Blaine has been training for this moment his entire life.

attributes.title: ELLIE PLAYS ELLIE - The Last of Us PART 1
attributes.description: Ellie & Jon had never played The Last of Us before which meant that Ellie had never played as Ellie and Jon had never been introduced into hot dad Joel. We are righting these wrongs today!

attributes.title: THE LAST OF THE ELLIES - The Last of Us PART 2
attributes.description: The apocalypse is just getting started and Ellie is getting used to making molotov cocktails out of any resources she can find.

attributes.title: NO ONE SCARE ELLIE! - The Last of Us PART 3
attributes.description: There were shenanigans during the last stream of The Last of Us. There will be no more shenanigans. If shenanigans ensue, Ellie will be writing a stern letter to your mother informing her of your transgressions.

attributes.title: TIME FOR MARIO FAMILY THERAPY - Super Mario Party
attributes.description: After this video, the men in this video got in their cars and never spoke to each other again.

attributes.title: ELLIE NEEDS A COCKTAIL - The Last of Us PART 4
attributes.description: Who knew that shivs were going to be so valuable in the coming apocalypse about fungus? We do now!

attributes.title: SHE MAKES HER OWN KNIVES - The Last of Us PART 5
attributes.description: We are getting close to the end now, supporting characters are dropping like flies, things are getting dark, and Ellie is getting pretty good at using the bow and arrow.

attributes.title: THE LAST OF THE LAST OF US OF US - The Last of Us PART 6
attributes.description: Everything has to have an ending. And some endings hit you so got damn hard in your emotions you need a moment to recover from how good the ending of The Last of Us is.

attributes.title: ROOSTER TEETH TEAM BUILDING - Super Mario Party
attributes.description: An important element of a healthy and efficiently functioning office environment is trust. Without it, productivity breaks down and chaos ensues. Why did we play this game again?

attributes.title: STEAL STARS FOR PROFIT - Super Mario Party
attributes.description: If someone has their stars stolen in a forest and nobody is around to hear his screams, does he make a sound?

attributes.title: THE BIRTH OF GAMBO - Super Mario Maker 2 PART 1
attributes.description: He's not a Goomba. He's a Gambo. And he is coming for you.

attributes.title: DARK SOULS OF WAR - God of War PART 2
attributes.description: We could turn the difficulty down at any time. Or we could watch Chad fight every creature in this game like it is a boss from Dark Souls.

attributes.title: MARIO DOES PUSHUPS - Super Mario Maker 2 PART 2
attributes.description: The Derp Crew joins the Rooster Teeth crew for some Mario Maker 2 and pushups.

attributes.title: SUPER CRINGE FAIL MAKER - Super Mario Maker 2 PART 3
attributes.description: We are so good this game. Thinking of going pro. Looking for brand sponsors right now.

attributes.title: STILL SCARED OF THE DARK - Visage PART 1
attributes.description: The bravest people at Rooster Teeth have decided to take on the horrors of Visage. Turns out the scariest thing is having to learn to use a keyboard to navigate the house of Visage.

attributes.title: GRANDMA LADY FROM HELL - Visage PART 2
attributes.description: Warning: watch your headphones on this one, the group playing screams...a lot. A lot a lot.

attributes.title: NUZLOCKE RUN - Pokemon Let's Go PART 1
attributes.description: Rooster Teeth is attempting a Nuzlocke Run on Pokemon Let's Go. It doesn't really work completely but it still sort of works perfectly.

attributes.title: WE FOUND ANA DE ARMAS! - Pokemon Let's Go PART 2
attributes.description: Rooster Teeth is attempting a Nuzlocke Run on Pokemon Let's Go. Our Pikachu is named Ana de Armas and she must be protected.

attributes.title: BEWARE THE DIGLETTS - Pokemon Let's Go PART 3
attributes.description: Rooster Teeth is attempting a Nuzlocke Run on Pokemon Let's Go. We fight Misty and meet up with maybe the worst Diglett ever.

attributes.title: I'M ON A BOAT! - Pokemon Let's Go PART 4
attributes.description: Rooster Teeth is attempting a Nuzlocke Run on Pokemon Let's Go. We complete the SS Anne and start heading to our next gym.

attributes.title: MAGIKARP EVOLVES? - Pokemon Let's Go PART 5
attributes.description: Rooster Teeth is attempting a Nuzlocke Run on Pokemon Let's Go. This week we mostly rock out in the Rock Tunnel for a while.

attributes.title: NOT JOHN MATRIX! - Pokemon Let's Go PART 6
attributes.description: Rooster Teeth is attempting a Nuzlocke Run on Pokemon Let's Go.

attributes.title: A REAL LIFE POKEMON - Pokemon Let's Go PART 7
attributes.description: Rooster Teeth is attempting a Nuzlocke Run on Pokemon Let's Go. Also, Dutch the dog takes over the entire stream basically.

attributes.title: WE BROKE VISAGE - Visage PART 3
attributes.description: We continue our run through the spooky world of Visage but it turns out the game is actually haunted so we had to swap to Mario Kart instead.

attributes.title: FOR THE GAMBO!! - World of Warcraft Classic PART 1
attributes.description: Say hello to Gambo. He loves two things. The Horde and chocolate chip cookie dough ice cream.

attributes.title: PERFECTLY TIMED CREEPER - Minecraft PART 1
attributes.description: Give a man a fish and he'll eat for a day. Teach a man to minecraft and he might build a shitty home that keeps getting blown up by Creepers.

attributes.title: WHY DID IT HAVE TO BE STAIRS? - Minecraft PART 2
attributes.description: Chris continues construction on his "house" and tackles two of the greatest Minecraft challenges there are: finding diamond and constructing a staircase.

attributes.title: BLAINE BUILDS A HOUSE - Minecraft PART 3
attributes.description: A new neighbor has moved into the area and he has plans on a better house than Chris. Which is honestly not a very lofty goal.
